{
  "texts": [
    "The following possible research lines can be considered, which could be materialized in future investigations through the use of GPT-3 in the field of education: incorporation of different types of questions in the content generation channel in different areas of educational knowledge, reflective dialogs between students and AI, and the creation of learning models based on AI with cooperative formats.",
    "The future of language models like GPT-3 seems promising, but it is also important to continue researching and improving in order to take full advantage of its potential.",
    "The review provides information on the use and applications of GPT-3 in the field of education, as well as certain limitations and challenges associated with the language model.",
    "GPT-3 has been shown to have valuable applications in education, but it still faces challenges and limitations that require additional research.",
    "It is crucial to address the biases (gender, currency, racial, geopolitical, etc.), to improve the performance in broader and structured contexts, and to find more affordable solutions for the use of pre-trained models in different applications."
  ]
}